<p><span style="font-size:18px">( Homebrew에 대한 설치방법과 자세한 설명은 출처: <a href="https://blog.naver.com/qkrtndus3062/222657808586">연님블로그 로 확인 해주세요. )</a></span><br />
<img src="https://images.velog.io/images/kyj0206/post/37cdaa61-547e-490e-8e4d-d28766d6962b/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202022-03-14%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AB%2011.12.47.png" alt="https://images.velog.io/images/kyj0206/post/37cdaa61-547e-490e-8e4d-d28766d6962b/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202022-03-14%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AB%2011.12.47.png" /></p>

<h4 id="2-jekyll-설치하기">2. Jekyll 설치하기.<br /></h4>

<p><span>테마 적용을 위한 파일을 가져오기 위해 jekyll을 설치해야 해줍니다.</span><br />
<img src="https://images.velog.io/images/kyj0206/post/68e1dd02-ace5-492b-8d86-bdbcb0e054a3/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202022-03-14%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AB%2010.55.57.png" alt="https://images.velog.io/images/kyj0206/post/68e1dd02-ace5-492b-8d86-bdbcb0e054a3/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202022-03-14%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AB%2010.55.57.png" /></p>

<h4 id="3-bundler-설치하기">3. bundler 설치하기.<br /></h4>
<p><span>bundler도 설치해줍시다.</span><br />
<img src="https://images.velog.io/images/kyj0206/post/46d2fd74-f3dc-46ef-8cbe-4e91c6c87422/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202022-03-14%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AB%2010.56.21.png" alt="https://images.velog.io/images/kyj0206/post/46d2fd74-f3dc-46ef-8cbe-4e91c6c87422/%E1%84%89%E1%85%B3%E1%84%8F%E1%85%B3%E1%84%85%E1%85%B5%E1%86%AB%E1%84%89%E1%85%A3%E1%86%BA%202022-03-14%20%E1%84%8B%E1%85%A9%E1%84%8C%E1%85%A5%E1%86%AB%2010.56.21.png" /></p>

